subject: College Athletics
Basketball
NCAA Basketball Tournament
lead_paragraph: Cornell beat Penn State, 83-58, on Friday to clinch a berth in the N.C.A.A. tournament for the second consecutive year, and Columbia defeated Princeton, 58-44.
